# Smart OPD System with Virtual Queue for Optimized Healthcare Delivery

## 📌 Project Overview
The **Smart OPD System** is a web-based healthcare management solution designed to automate and optimize outpatient services. It offers features like virtual queue scheduling, AI-powered disease prediction, chatbot support, and real-time hospital resource tracking.

Developed as part of a final year B.Tech project in **Computer Science Engineering (Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning)**, the system aims to improve patient care, reduce waiting times, and streamline hospital administration.

---

## 🚀 Key Features
- 🧠 **AI-Based Disease Prediction** using Support Vector Machine (SVM)
- ⏳ **Virtual Queue Management** based on patient priority
- 🛏️ **Real-Time Bed Availability Tracking**
- 💬 **NLP Chatbot (NutriBot)** for diet and symptom-based medical assistance
- 👨‍⚕️ **Role-Based Access Control** (Admin, Doctor, Patient)
- 📋 **Appointment Booking & Consultation Tracking**
- 📈 **Admin Dashboard** with statistics and reports

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

| Component        | Technology                   |
|------------------|------------------------------|
| Frontend         | HTML, CSS, JavaScript        |
| Backend          | Django (Python)              |
| Database         | SQLite                       |
| AI/ML Libraries  | Scikit-Learn, TensorFlow     |
| Chatbot NLP      | Custom NLP with Python       |
| REST API Testing | Postman                      |
| Version Control  | Git & GitHub                 |

---

## 🧠 Machine Learning

### 🎯 Models Used
- **Support Vector Machine (SVM)** for:
  - Heart Disease Prediction
  - Diabetes Prediction
  - Parkinson’s Disease Prediction

### 📊 Datasets
| Disease         | Dataset Source     | Records | Features Used                     |
|----------------|--------------------|---------|-----------------------------------|
| Heart Disease  | UCI Cleveland      | ~303    | Age, Cholesterol, ECG, BP, etc.   |
| Diabetes       | PIMA Indian        | ~768    | Glucose, BMI, Insulin, Pregnancies|
| Parkinson’s    | UCI Parkinson’s    | ~195    | Vocal features, jitter, frequency |

---

## 📂 Modules

### 👤 Patient Module
- Register/Login
- Book Appointments
- Access NutriBot Chatbot
- View Reports and Medical History

### 🩺 Doctor Module
- View Appointment Queue
- Predict Disease Using ML
- Record Diagnosis & Prescriptions

### 🛠️ Admin Module
- Manage Doctor Profiles & Schedules
- Monitor Appointments & Beds
- Generate Reports & Stats

---

## 🛠️ Installation & Setup

### Requirements
- Python 3.8+
- pip
- Virtualenv (optional)

### Steps
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/smart-opd-system.git
cd smart-opd-system
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
